'''''eneth''''' is a noun meaning "name" in [[Sindarin]].
==Etymology==
The etymology of this word is obscure. It is unknown if it contains any [[Sundocarmë|Root]] related to the [[Quenya]] word ''[[Essë|esse]]''.

Note that the verb "to name" in Sindarin is ''[[esta-]]''.
